'''Pierre Zimmermann''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.
Zimmermann has competed as Pierre Zimmerman.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[World Transnational Open Teams Championship]] (2) 2007, 2009 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/transnational-open-teams.aspx World Transational Open Teams Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (5)
